      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAMSET READY (3) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (18.70) at this track in a Maiden. Lines up from box 3 for the first time. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Can measure up this time. HELLO NEMO (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 1.75 lengths into second (18.36) at this track in a Grade 5 over 320m. The form from his last run stacks up well. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. HOODWINKED (2) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey having won two of three starts. Recorded a 6 length win (19.34) in a Grade 5 last time at Bulli. Can feature with the right run. HELPING HAND (6) scored with plenty to spare last time. Hard to beat again.",
